Package com.flipkart.DAO

Interface SlotInterfaceDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SlotDAO
    public interface SlotInterfaceDAO
    This interface defines the data access operations related to Slot functionality. It includes methods for retrieving slot lists, adding slots, and retrieving slots based on center and slot IDs.
